public class UserDataResponse

isLimitedData

public boolean isLimitedData()
Returns true if Janrain Engage was able to retrieve only limited public data from the user's profile (e.g., because the login session has expired or the user logged out from their account). If Janrain Engage succeeded in retrieving complete set of data, this field will be set to false. Used only with Facebook.
